CoD servers management.

cli - Old python command-line only script.

codadmin - new Webui based on Django

------------
    DOC
------------

https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/1.3/


------------
DEVELOPEMENT
------------

Install django libs on ubuntu:

  sudo aptitude install python-django

Clone repository
   git clone http://github.com/cheuveulu/LANBox.git
Got to codadmin folder
   cd LANBox/codadmin

* First time :
   python manager.py syncdb

Run web server
   python manager.py runserver 0.0.0.0:8000


Happy hacking
